in Beijing

49
00:02:17,340 --> 00:02:21,549
and that officials tied to Jiang Zemin tried
to stage a coup.

50
00:02:21,549 --> 00:02:25,189
And while the actual gunshots were never confirmed,
years later,

51
00:02:25,189 --> 00:02:29,519
a Party official publicly said that several
people in Jiang’s

52
00:02:29,519 --> 00:02:32,769
faction did try to get rid of Xi Jinping.

53
00:02:32,769 --> 00:02:36,719
All those people are coincidentally now in
prison.

54
00:02:36,719 --> 00:02:38,719
Funny how that happens.

55
00:02:38,719 --> 00:02:41,389
So will these latest rumors be confirmed?

56
00:02:41,389 --> 00:02:42,529
I don’t think so.

57
00:02:42,529 --> 00:02:47,079
It’s next to impossible for there to be
a Jiang-Hu alliance.

58
00:02:47,079 --> 00:02:51,060
But, another attempt by Jiang’s faction
to stage a coup,

59
00:02:51,060 --> 00:02:53,529
