60
00:02:53,529 --> 00:02:55,489
One thing the rumors do show though,

61
00:02:55,489 --> 00:02:58,879
is that the factional struggle within the
Chinese Communist Party

62
00:02:58,879 --> 00:03:00,510
is alive and well.

63
00:03:00,510 --> 00:03:04,340
Can’t wait for the next episode of General
Hostility.

64
00:03:04,340 --> 00:03:07,489
So those coup rumors may just be lies.

65
